Package: RTrade
Type: Package
Title: Backtesting of Trading Strategies
Version: 0.2.7
Author: Pankaj Sharma
Maintainer: <psharma@incurrency.com>
Description: The package provides 1. Ability to retrieve equity and futures prices from kairosdb, hosted by incurrency. 2. basic vector manipulation utilities that are useful for backtesting. 3. Framework for backtesting of trading signals. 4. Bootstrapping of trades. Added flag in bootstrap to reinstate tradingsize after target drawdown period.
License: BSD-3-clause
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
